</P>
<P>
   &QR;  OTHER ACTIVITIES _ Scuba diving and snorkeling are excellent
and can be arranged through travel agents. Touring the small island
in a car can take a day or more, but will give you the flavor of
the old Puerto Rico of small farms and villages. Sidetrips to El
Yunque, a mountainous tropical rainforest, and the Arecibo
Observatory, a giant radio telescope where NASA searches for
extra-terrestrial life, are highly recommended.
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
