   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   ABERNATHY-TRIAL (Atlanta) _ The case of Ralph Abernathy, son of
the civil rights leader, goes to the jury. He is charged with
stealing money as a state senator, but maintains the charges are
politically motivated. He is son of civil rights leader.
</P>
<P>
   NC-TIRE-STRIKE (Undated) _ Steelworkers settle a year-long
strike involving 1,400 workers against a tire manufacuturer in
Charlotte, N.C. By Steven Greenhouse.
