<P>
   TIMOR-U.N. (United Nations) _ On the day that the Security
Council voted to send a multinational force into East Timor to
restore order and protect relief operations, U.N. relief workers
began to assess the needs of tens of thousands of East Timorese
driven from their homes in almost two weeks of violence prompted by
