officials, take part in a news conference denouncing the Republican
tax cut on Wednesday. Joining three other top city Democrats, Mrs.
Clinton and Ferrer stood shoulder to shoulder during the news
conference, an apparent symbol of her desire to mend fences with
the Puerto Rican community after she angered many of them by
opposing the clemency granted by President Clinton to a group of
