<P>
   (NYT1) ATLANTA, Ga. -- Sept. 15, 1999 -- KIDS-GARDENS-COX, 09-15
-- Kieran Maynard, 9, right, and his brother Pace Maynard, 7,
enjoys the Sunflower fountain at the new Children's Garden at the
Atlanta Botanical Gardens last Thursday. Public gardens around the
country are developing programs that not only expose future
generations to the joys of plants but, on a more practical level,
help the new gardens help generate more income from admissions.
(William Berry/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
</P>
