</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Get Real: An inside look at Saturn
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _
</P>
<P>
   Real name: Perry Saturn.
</P>
<P>
   Ht., wt.: 5-9, 234.
</P>
<P>
   Hometown: Boston.
</P>
<P>
   Debut: 1992.
</P>
<P>
   Finishing move: Death Valley Driver, Rings of Saturn.
</P>
<P>
   Did you know? Was a member of the U.S. Army Airborne Rangers ...
Trained at Killer Kowalski's wrestling school, which also produced
Triple H. ... Once dated Chyna. ... Appeared in the music video
``Jump Around'' by House of Pain.
</P>
<P>
   Titles: WCW Tag, WCW TV, ECW Tag (3).
